		Create Username </h5>
		<input class="textbox" type="text" placeholder="    Enter Username" name="uname" required>
		<br>
		<h5 class="newAccount texts"> Password </h5>
		<h5 style="display: none" class="newAccount texts"> 
		Create Password </h5>
		<input style="margin-bottom: 0px" class="textbox" type="password" placeholder="    Enter Password" name="psw" required>
